# =============================================================================
#  DATA NEVER GOES IN THIS REPO.
#  The AGO exports, priority sheets, manifests, and backups contain student and
#  faculty emails, names, login history, and graduation status -- education
#  records. They live in institutional storage, not here. The blanket rules
#  below are deliberately aggressive; if you ever need a small synthetic fixture
#  committed, force it with `git add -f` and be sure it contains no real data.
# =============================================================================

# ---- Raw ArcGIS Online exports ----
*Organization*Items*.csv
*Organization*Members*.csv
*OrganizationItemUsages*.csv
*OrganizationActivity*.csv
*Activity*.csv
members*.csv

# ---- Working priority / tracking sheets ----
cleanup_priority*.csv
priority*.csv
email_list*.csv
*departed*.csv
*graduat*.csv

# ---- Run artifacts: manifests, results, review lists, write-backs ----
cleanup_manifest*.csv
cleanup_results*.csv
cleanup_review*.csv
*_updated.csv

# ---- Blanket catch-alls (belt and suspenders) ----
*.csv
*.tsv
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.gdb
*.gdb.zip
*.zip

# ---- Working directories (keep the folder, drop the contents) ----
data/**
!data/README.md
outputs/**
!outputs/.gitkeep
backups/**
!backups/.gitkeep

# ---- Credentials / local config with real values ----
config.py
config.local.*
*.local.*
.env
*.token
*.key
*credentials*
*secret*

# ---- R / Python / editor cruft ----
.Rhistory
.RData
.Rproj.user/
*.Rproj
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.DS_Store